questions.question: What are the main benefits your company has seen in adopting the cloud?

subQuestions.subquestion: Consistency, everything is done the same way on the same system
Reliability, the system is always up and running
Easier to support other internal departments (finance, sales, marketing,etc)
Better support for strategic decision making
Limits employee use of non-approved (shadow) IT
Allows us to be more innovative
Allows us to bring products to market faster
Allows us to implement new business models
Allows us to target and attract new customers
